with info    home http://www.karlrunge.com/x11vnc/
with info    cite 'vnc server
x11vnc allows one to view remotely and interact with real X displays
(i.e. a display corresponding to a physical monitor, keyboard, and mouse)
with any VNC viewer.
In this way it plays thewit role    for Unix/X11 that WinVNC plays for Windows.'
